text: Terrorism and Kebab (, transliterated: Al-irhab wal kabab) is a 1992 Egyptian black comedy movie directed by Sherif Arafah and also starring Adel Emam, Yousra, Kamal el-Shennawi, Ahmed Rateb. ==Other websites== * Category:1992 comedy movies Category:1990s black comedy movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies directed by Sherif Arafah
